# Satellite repos — one per line, format: prefix|directory-name
# Paths are relative to the parent directory of this Spire hub.
#
# Example: if your hub is at ~/projects/spire and your web app is at
# ~/projects/my-web-app, add:
#
#   web|my-web-app
#
# Each satellite gets:
#   - A .beads/redirect pointing to the hub's database
#   - Routes for cross-repo visibility
#   - A SPIRE_IDENTITY in .envrc
#   - Cursor MCP server config (if using Cursor)
#
# Re-run setup.sh after editing this file.

# web|my-web-app
# api|my-api-server
# infra|my-infrastructure
